{"type": "article", "id": 35614, "title": "Gucci硬照越来越有马戏团风格，以及，陈冠希要在北京办展 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2016-12-15T02:43:46Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 671, "name": "Gucci"}, {"id": 2636, "name": "Swatch"}, {"id": 3112, "name": "Bally"}, {"id": 14105, "name": "porter"}, {"id": 35848, "name": "TMT"}, {"id": 1548, "name": "开云集团"}, {"id": 17411, "name": "陈冠希"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 36, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161215102908f5QoGSB6yilO39Lv.png", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.cpp-luxury.com/bally-to-launch-in-india/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>瑞士品牌 Bally 将进军印度市场</b></a> | Bally 将与印度最大的私营公司 Reliance Group 的子公司 Reliance Brands Ltd 合作，计划明年在印度新德里开设第一家门店，接着进驻孟买，加尔各答，金奈。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://footwearnews.com/2016/business/news/kering-14-week-paid-maternity-leave-285692/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>奢侈品集团开云许诺要给员工 14 周的带薪产假</b></a> | 开云集团宣布，员工中生产或者是收养小孩的，可以休最少 14 个周的带薪产假。符合条件的员工需要在开云集团工作一年以上，不论职位高低和所在地区。目前，开云集团在全球 60 多个国家和地区，共有 38500 名员工。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/technology/emarketer-digital-banking-trends-10727443/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>明年，至少有 60% 的美国消费者将使用在线银行支付功能</b></a> | 市场研究机构 Emarketer 预测，到 2017 年，将至少有 60% 的美国人，使用在线银行支付功能。有大约 1.5 亿的美国成年人，每个月至少使用一次在线支付功能——哎呀，他们是比我们落后很多，不要笑。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>Gucci 近几年的宣传大片越来越像是马戏团风格的艺术作品，继奇幻之旅之后，<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2016/12/14/gucci-ss17-campaign/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gucci 发布了它的 2017 春夏系列宣传大片</a>，狮子、老虎、长颈鹿等野生动物悉数登场。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215101143vIZzXpray4YJS1q8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.830206\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215101150VkJ9nyO7EzNLiSlT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.830206\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215101151zjBCec0p5W9LUqVJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.830206\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215101155zxlK58OaC37IeYmL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.830206\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215101155L6uZMKhVC5nRIz1S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.830206\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215101157fw1an9Sz5ZJtxEqA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.830206\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215103009DzuxCaANik3XrVlJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.830206\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215103008zQ1qms6X8M3BnPVw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.830206\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215101219m94ozdGMn0Hjrixl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.527458\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215101231DjYbMw9rUIXkTmPB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.527458\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215101236PgL74nuAMyBjR8tp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499361\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/12/swatch-2016-xmas\" rel=\"nofollow\">Swatch 今年的圣诞限定腕表</a>，以淡蓝色为主调，点缀着雪花图案，包装盒则像是一个北欧的小屋一样。这款腕表现已发售，全球限量 8888 枚。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215101052OwiWUGsgePcTHxk0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215101122XVLoy5sfzC1bwHIA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215101122aoTWcyBipSMKjdlt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215101129NZR1T9KFb7GWxJq6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/12/porter-local\" rel=\"nofollow\">Porter 发布 2016 秋冬 Local 系列</a>，在材质上运用了 60% 棉和 40% 的厚牛津布搭配制成，全系列包括黑、浅灰、杏色和咖啡色四种颜色，将于 12 月 16 日正式发售。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215101033ftIezgcbKjsnd56O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215101032aS1ZkBKMcU8XGYDT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612151010335cJiqsGTfagF2dR7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612151010335vJQsiNLhlEBco08.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215101043YGI6E4OzxcZyXfNi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215101043AwbzdSnN8a04tcBE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>继香港、洛杉矶和东京之后，陈冠希首次把他的<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/12/edison-chen-3125c-ucca-pop-up\" rel=\"nofollow\"> 3125C 艺术企划</a>带到内地，他将与北京尤伦斯艺术商店合作，在 12 月 16 日开设全新的快闪店，这个店将同步展出陈冠希的个人摄影展，独家发售与艺术家合作的服饰单品，持续到明年 1 月中旬结束。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215100925ZIxaKHoC2bUeGN39.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215100942jZubqesPnmy3pch6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215100942nFyCo8T6ZpcNasrR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667236\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215100951B5lTkKRJvVFtc3z0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215101010VPClUSGZRDs75vym.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612151010196Unt8MBo2lijmGrA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215101101O5lx7MsDzvFmi2Lo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215101108ACrzZ4eflPwcIbdM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">喜欢美式复古潮流的话，不妨来看一下日本品牌 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/12/tmt-2016-fall-winter-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">TMT 的 2016 秋冬造型特辑</a>。TMT 以坚持日本制造的美式休闲复古而著称，也是木村拓哉爱用的品牌。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215101252L1JXiRZVj2DmvznN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612151012510kZPpHbOtX2nTChr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215101251pjnMi7dkWtx1GUcy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215101252ClxD79oGhFfutWsQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215101252jw3KWAXM1rnaLRZy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215101252ou5Cevm2t1siglFX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215101301Db9PNHCfymaRtnkL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p>"}